    http-push: push <remote> :<branch> deletes remote branch
    
    This mirrors current ssh/git push syntax.
    
    Signed-off-by: Clemens Buchacher <drizzd@aon.at>
    Signed-off-by: Junio C Hamano <gitster@pobox.com>

